28:03.540 --> 28:05.820
Frederick Poe has every reason to be proud.

28:06.380 --> 28:09.420
He has either produced or helped produce some of the masterworks of science fiction.

28:10.040 --> 28:13.640
Through being an editor he has helped discover and develop some of today's best writers.

